    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >这是一封给大家的道歉信</h2>   大家好，我们是《天神印》项目组。首先，我们要向所有支持我们的玩家致以最诚挚的歉意。我们认识到，《天神印》并未达到市场的期望，也不符合一款合格游戏的要求。<br>   在此我们向大家真挚的道歉。为了不给国产独立游戏行业造成困扰和debuff，共同维护独立游戏圈的和谐氛围，巩固彼此之间的信任。也为了弥补玩家的损失，并表达我们的诚意和歉意。我们决定，在游戏完善至达到收费标准之前：<br>   <strong> 将《天神印》改为免费游戏，并为之前购买游戏的玩家提供退款服务。<br>   我们已向Steam提交了关于改变收费模式的审核申请，预计一周后商店页面将转为免费。</strong><br>自《天神印》上线之后，我们始终密切观察着市场的反应。接踵而来的各个评价都既在我们的预期之外，也在我们的预料之中，一切都显得那么合情合理。<br>说是在预期之外，是因为项目组在此期间投入了大量的精力和资金，在截止上线之前的这三年中，其中的运营成本已经超过445w人民币。在此期间游戏共推翻五次，最终展现给大家的是八月底开始制作的第六版，也是最终版本。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/06fdc50c5112affbd43ec0284ef1772a.poster.avif?t=1706712229\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/06fdc50c5112affbd43ec0284ef1772a.webm?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/06fdc50c5112affbd43ec0284ef1772a.mp4?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/34123786b039b659861cc300d97590ee.poster.avif?t=1706712229\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/34123786b039b659861cc300d97590ee.webm?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/34123786b039b659861cc300d97590ee.mp4?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/f92aee5520422c496ff2394969c093ba.poster.avif?t=1706712229\" width=420 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/f92aee5520422c496ff2394969c093ba.webm?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/f92aee5520422c496ff2394969c093ba.mp4?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/4a91c4bd6567aabee80a14fa9f6fec1f.poster.avif?t=1706712229\" width=420 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/4a91c4bd6567aabee80a14fa9f6fec1f.webm?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/4a91c4bd6567aabee80a14fa9f6fec1f.mp4?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/6ec23dafbfad1685953d80dab3c6e968.poster.avif?t=1706712229\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/6ec23dafbfad1685953d80dab3c6e968.webm?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/6ec23dafbfad1685953d80dab3c6e968.mp4?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>   说在预料之中，是因为由于项目组在游戏开发初期过于缺乏经验，项目组内人员多为没有任何行业经验的游戏热爱者。导致游戏在游戏性和美术表现上均未能达到预期水平。<br>   我们已深刻认识到当前游戏的不足，夜不能寐。在深刻的反思之后，我们汲取了之前的失败教训，并坚决避免重蹈覆辙。<strong>目前我们已启动了全新的项目：《除岁》。 <br> 《除岁》是一款国风横版射击游戏，它会更加聚焦，且具有可执行性，目前项目已经完成立项，正在紧锣密鼓地制作demo。</strong>预计一年之后上线。在此，我们恳请玩家们给予更多的理解和支持，共同见证我们的成长与进步。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/2305411aefee0b11d98179e2d459fbbd.avif?t=1706712229\" width=768 height=446 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/9ef666c3fbeca559a051265f2c633e2f.avif?t=1706712229\" width=800 height=286 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/dcf29cfb2d724c2a2d510fbfd082984e.avif?t=1706712229\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras_big/dcf29cfb2d724c2a2d510fbfd082984e.avif?t=1706712229 width=800 height=332 /></span><br><br>   为了《除岁》项目能够做的更好，我们建立了《除岁》项目QQ群，邀请感兴趣的玩家加入。我们诚挚地欢迎玩家们为我们提供宝贵的建议，与我们共同探讨。<br> <strong>《除岁》项目交流QQ群：677522088<br>   同时我们保证，不会放弃我们做的第一款游戏，《天神印》始终都会保持更新。</strong><br>   由于《天神印》框架建构冗杂。在更新时，我们需要填补大量的内容，包括且不止与地图、文案、剧情、道具、野怪、BOSS、技能、技艺、心法等一系列内容。因此更新时间间隔会比较长。也希望各位可以多多为我们提供建议，让它变得更好。同时，也让项目组变得更好。<br>最后，再次向所有玩家表示歉意和感谢。我们希望能够通过努力和改进，重新赢得玩家的信任和喜爱。<br>   <strong>我们始终坚信，唯有热爱，可抵岁月漫长。</strong><br>  《天神印》项目组敬上。<br><br>----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1、关于游戏</h2>   神魔大战之后，天道法则突变，天雷早降让人间修士无从防备，一代骄子尽皆陨落。往后数十年，竟无一人突破炼气之境。修仙之路一时萧条。万年之后，桃花村内，少年秦霄满怀豪情，不顾父母劝阻，决意踏上修仙之途。<br>   凭借着卓越的天赋，秦霄顺利拜入修仙山门。然而，修仙之路艰险无比，随着时间的推移，不仅秦霄的修为日益精进，更有一群强大的对手陆续出现在他的面前，阻碍着他前进的道路。随着桃花仙的陨落、句芒的消失、大阵的损毁，前方却越加扑朔迷离。<br>在女帝城中，秦霄遭遇了被囚禁于锁妖塔中万年之久的大妖九尾，她虽美艳绝伦，却手段狠辣，无数修士丧命其手。经过艰苦努力，秦霄终于击败九尾，然而这仅仅是真相的冰山一角。神魔大战的真相、天道突变的原因、无故陨落的上神秦天、还有，这断绝通神之路的天神印...还将有更多的未知在等待秦霄。在这无情的天道之下，再没人能从无尽的旋涡之中逃离。<br><br>----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2、关于我们</h2>    官方\tQ群：839142973 欢迎各位道友的加入。<br><br>----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3、游戏介绍模块</h2><strong>①地图系统</strong><br>在《天神印》这款游戏中，玩家将置身于一个广袤无垠的大地图，自由探索，任意前行，不断揭示新的地域和壮丽的景观。这个世界美轮美奂，展现出多重环境，仿佛是一个梦中桃源。桃花林若隐若现，恍若人间仙境；火山地壳下的熔岩汹涌，狂野而炽热；鹿吴峭壁巍峨耸立，展示着大自然的雄壮；贾超密林深邃幽暗，隐藏着无尽的奥秘。<br>每个环境都拥有独特的天气模式，为探索之旅增添了丰富的变化。玩家在游戏中可以与环境中的各种物体和地形进行互动。无论是采集珍稀的草药还是挖掘珍贵的矿石，每一次互动都可能带来意想不到的收获。同时，要警惕那些出人意料的陷阱和隐秘的地图入口，它们可能会为你的冒险之旅带来新的挑战和惊喜。在这个广袤而多彩的世界中，探索、冒险与发现将成为《天神印》的主题。<br><br><strong>地图功能展示：</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/babe48d7300a26a8a276770b612af2b2.poster.avif?t=1706712229\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/babe48d7300a26a8a276770b612af2b2.webm?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/babe48d7300a26a8a276770b612af2b2.mp4?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>人物移动展示：</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/fbbd348d0581e482c0381c88e3130a09.poster.avif?t=1706712229\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/fbbd348d0581e482c0381c88e3130a09.webm?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/fbbd348d0581e482c0381c88e3130a09.mp4?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/7face91d5bfb5ef0c5377042b60f2385.poster.avif?t=1706712229\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/7face91d5bfb5ef0c5377042b60f2385.webm?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/7face91d5bfb5ef0c5377042b60f2385.mp4?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/fb20cc18b0f1a141ec8f516f4fa24f1d.poster.avif?t=1706712229\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/fb20cc18b0f1a141ec8f516f4fa24f1d.webm?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/fb20cc18b0f1a141ec8f516f4fa24f1d.mp4?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>②神墓系统</strong><br>地图中散落传说中的神魔墓入口。玩家可以通过寻找来揭示这些秘密。但是，只有找到入口是不够的，你还需要打败墓穴的主人，从而获得珍稀的奖励和更加深入的了解游戏世界的故事。在这个过程中，你们将面临前所未有的挑战，但也将收获无尽的乐趣与成就感。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/1e158f768ab03b936b7a47f220ce1339.poster.avif?t=1706712229\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/1e158f768ab03b936b7a47f220ce1339.webm?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/1e158f768ab03b936b7a47f220ce1339.mp4?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/569480024c1c079a805dbf1f34fe6776.poster.avif?t=1706712229\" width=500 height=281 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/569480024c1c079a805dbf1f34fe6776.webm?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/e25d0fdb1103690f640c711e83508926.poster.avif?t=1706712229\" width=500 height=281 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/e25d0fdb1103690f640c711e83508926.webm?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/051dfac9e82919d47fc34d7afa20e9f4.poster.avif?t=1706712229\" width=500 height=281 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/051dfac9e82919d47fc34d7afa20e9f4.webm?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>③技能流派</strong><br>技能系统根据灵气属性不同，分为金、木、水、火、土五套系统技能，并各有不同的专属武器。除此之外，还有雷、风、冰三系额外的附属技能。一并为玩家提供了丰富的技能选择和搭配可能性。玩家可以根据自己的游戏风格和需求，自由组合各种技能，创造出独特的战斗方式。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/40ec1882639625fbf6560119a5910048.poster.avif?t=1706712229\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/40ec1882639625fbf6560119a5910048.webm?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/40ec1882639625fbf6560119a5910048.mp4?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>④技艺系统</strong><br>技艺系统作为《天神印》中的一大特色玩法，为游戏带来了更加丰富的层次和深度。它独立于技能系统，使玩家能够探索和学习独特的技艺，例如画符、炼丹、铸造等。<br>通过学习和掌握这些技艺，玩家在战斗中将更具优势，能够更有效地应对敌人。丰富了游戏的玩法，还为玩家提供了更多的自由度和选择空间。玩家可以根据自己的喜好和游戏需求，选择学习和掌握不同的技艺，打造出独具特色的角色。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/51e14edd4c41607ddec89e3280d504be.poster.avif?t=1706712229\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/51e14edd4c41607ddec89e3280d504be.webm?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/51e14edd4c41607ddec89e3280d504be.mp4?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/c1c7f1d0f1c61e30cc1d27b4a6ebb9ad.poster.avif?t=1706712229\" width=500 height=281 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/c1c7f1d0f1c61e30cc1d27b4a6ebb9ad.webm?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/15ea0dd6e7f40315824ea5c54b1fe73f.poster.avif?t=1706712229\" width=500 height=281 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361240/extras/15ea0dd6e7f40315824ea5c54b1fe73f.webm?t=1706712229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
